title: Rush - Working Men [320k MP3]
description:
Working Men is a live compilation album by Canadian progressive rock band Rush. The compilation documents a shortlist of career-spanning material pulled from the band's three tours during the 2000s. The selections are from the Vapor Trails Tour, the R30: 30th Anniversary Tour and the Snakes & Arrows Tour. 

Track Listing [320k MP3]

01. 	"Limelight" (From Snakes & Arrows Live (2008)) 
02. 	"The Spirit of Radio" (From R30: 30th Anniversary World Tour (2005)) 	
03. 	"2112: Overture/The Temples of Syrinx" (From Rush in Rio (2003)) 
04. 	"Freewill" (From Snakes & Arrows Live) 
05. 	"Dreamline" (From R30) 
06. 	"Far Cry" (From Snakes & Arrows Live) 	
07. 	"Subdivisions" (From R30) 	
08. 	"One Little Victory" (Previously unreleased; recorded during the R30) 	
09. 	"Closer to the Heart" (From Rush in Rio; lyrics by Peart/Peter Talbot) 	
10. 	"Tom Sawyer" (From Snakes & Arrows Live; lyrics by Peart/Pye Dubois) 	
11. 	"Working Man" (From R30; Music and lyrics by Lee/Lifeson) 
12. 	"YYZ" (From Rush in Rio; Music by Lee/Peart)
